          case  $variable-name  in
                pattern1)       
     		    command1
                    ...
                    ....
                    commandN
                    ;;
                pattern2)
     		    command1
                    ...
                    ....
                    commandN
                    ;;            
                patternN)       
     		    command1
                    ...
                    ....
                    commandN
                    ;;
                *)              
          esac

This is the syntax of the case loop. Wildcards can be used  
